text: The food here is delicious! Especially the dry spicy vinegar beef noodles, highly recommended! The chef is so friendly and gave us a popcorn chicken! Although is a bit far, but worth it to come here eat!

The fried rice tasted great (even without the need for condiments). Also recommended are side dishes such as the Fried Dumplings, Pork Chop and Popcorn Chicken are tasty and crispy, without the need for condiments too. Thumbs up.
Fantastic food, loved the pork chop as it tastes extremely tender and delicious!
